==典礼资讯==
{{double image|right|Alec Baldwin at the 2010 SAG Awards.jpg|140|Steve Martin 2011.jpg|150|[[亚历克·鲍德温|亚历克·鲍德温]]（左）和[[史提夫·馬丁|史提夫·馬丁]]共同主持第82届奥斯卡颁奖典礼}}
由于前几届奥斯卡颁奖典礼的收视率出现下滑，因此学院希望可以采取措施重振奖项和晚会的声威，引起人们对提名电影的兴趣。[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|之前一年的颁奖典礼]]在收视人数上相比[[第80届奥斯卡金像奖|再前一年]]有13%的提高，学院内的许多成员于是提出了一些有望让奖项更受欢迎的新方案。当时的学院主席西德尼·甘尼斯宣布，本届奥斯卡金像奖角逐中最佳影片的提名电影将由以往沿用多年的5部提高到10部。“10个最佳影片提名将让学院投票成员们得以认可一些通常会角逐其它奖项，但却无缘最高奖的优异电影。”<ref name="Academy PR" />“我都等不及想看到2月公布提名名单时十部（最佳影片提名作品）的名单会是什么样了。”<ref name="Academy PR" />甘尼斯还表示，这也会让预测最终胜出作品变得更困难，因为投票规则将需要由[[多數制|多數制]]改为[[排序複選制|排序複選制]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8539436.stm |title=BBC News: Oscars 2010: Best picture voting changes explained |last=Smith |first=Neil |publisher=BBC |work=BBC News |date=2010-03-01 |accessdate=2013-11-04 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130620065333/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8539436.stm | archivedate= 2013-06-20 | deadurl= no}}</ref>

[[編舞|編舞]]比尔·麦康尼克和亚当·山克曼获聘成为晚会的[[制片人|制片人]]。山克曼曾在一次接受[[全国公共广播电台|全国公共广播电台]]节目采访时透露，自己和麦康尼克起初选择了[[沙查·巴隆·科恩|沙查·巴隆·科恩]]担任主持人，但学院否决了这一提议，因为科恩“这步棋实在太险了”。<ref name="hosting">{{cite web |url=http://www.npr.org/templates/transcript/transcript.php?storyId=123844321 |title=Shankman's Winning Job: Producing The Oscars |date=2010-02-18 |work=National Public Radio |publisher=National Public Radio |accessdate=2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20111227010144/http://www.npr.org/templates/transcript/transcript.php?storyId=123844321 | archivedate= 2011-12-27 | deadurl= no}}</ref>

许多在之前一年获得好评的做法得以保持下来，男、女主角奖的颁奖嘉宾均为5人，每一人介绍一位获提名演员的表演。山克曼和麦康尼克宣布，他们有意缩短电视转播的时长<ref>{{cite news |title=Looking Forward to The Big Show |first=Nicole |last=Sperling |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2010-02-12}}</ref>。这一年大部分颁奖嘉宾宣布获奖者时的用词都由“而获奖者是……”改为了“而奥斯卡奖属于……”，上一次出现这一情况则是在1988年举行的[[第60届奥斯卡金像奖|第60届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]。学院没有对这一改动作出解释，这一做法一度让其他没有获奖的提名人感到羞辱，但显然，学院还是默许了两位制片人让颁奖词回归老传统的做法。<ref>{{cite news|archivedate=2013-11-05 |url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1971420,00.html |title=An Oscar Comeback: 'And the Winner Is ...' |work=Time |publisher=Time Warner |last=Alexander |first=Bryan |date=2010-03-08 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105033129/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1971420%2C00.html }}</ref>

=== 提名电影票房表现 ===
在本届奥斯卡金像奖角逐中获最佳影片提名的十部电影中，有五数在提名公布前就已经在美国和[[加拿大|加拿大]]收获了超过1亿[[美元|美元]]的[[票房|票房]]，这是继2003年以来主要奖项提名作品中首次出现至少一部[[大片|大片]]<ref name="laetoscars">{{cite news | last = Horn | first = John | coauthors = | title = Oscar nominations that are for the people | publisher= Tribune Company| work = Los Angeles Times | date = 2010-02-03 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2010/feb/03/entertainment/la-et-oscars-main3-2010feb03 | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131022132630/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/feb/03/entertainment/la-et-oscars-main3-2010feb03 | archivedate= 2013-10-22 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。多位评论员、[[记者|记者]]和娱乐业人士分析认为，学院将最佳影片提名数量从五部增加到十部是大片得以获得主要奖项提名的重要原因<ref name="laetoscars" /><ref>{{cite news | last = Grat | first = Brandon | coauthors = | title = 2009 Academy Award Nominations | work = ''Box Office Mojo''| publisher = Amazon.com | date = 2010-02-02 | url = http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2666&p=.htm | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131019091746/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2666&p=.htm | archivedate= 2013-10-19 | deadurl= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Spiegel | first = Josh | coauthors = | title = In Contention | work = Box Office Prophets | publisher = Box Office Prophets | date = 2010-02-09 | url = http://www.boxofficeprophets.com/column/index.cfm?columnID=12535 | accessdate = 2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131019224019/http://www.boxofficeprophets.com/column/index.cfm?columnID=12535 | archivedate= 2013-10-19 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

提名公布时，十部获最佳影片提名的电影中有三部位于电影票房榜的前十位。其中《阿凡达》以5.96亿美元的美国票房名列榜首，也是年度电影票房[[冠军|冠军]]<ref name="laetoscars" />，其他两部美国电影票房排行榜十强中获提名的还有是收入2.93亿美元的《飞屋环游记》<ref name="laetoscars" />和收入2.38亿美元的《弱点》<ref name="laetoscars" />。剩下的七部提名作品中，《无耻混蛋》以1.2亿美元票房排在第一<ref name="laetoscars" />，《第9区》以1.16亿美元紧随其后<ref name="laetoscars" />，接下来分别是收入7300万美元的《在云端》<ref name="desertnewsoscars" />，4500万美元的《珍爱人生》<ref name="desertnewsoscars" />，1200万美元的《拆弹部队》<ref name="desertnewsoscars" />，940万美元的《成长教育》<ref name="desertnewsoscars">{{cite web |archivedate=2013-10-16 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.deseretnews.com/article/700006507/Box-office-numbers-for-Oscar-best-picture-nominees.html |title=Box-office numbers for Oscar best-picture nominees |publisher=Deseret Management Corporation |work=Deseret News |accessdate=2013-11-05 |date=2010-02-02 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131016010124/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/700006507/Box-office-numbers-for-Oscar-best-picture-nominees.html}}</ref>和920万美元的《严肃的男人》<ref name="desertnewsoscars" />。

在2009年美国电影票房最高的50部电影中，有13部电影获得了共计46项提名。其中《阿凡达》（冠军）、《飞屋环游记》（第5名）、《弱点》（第8名）、《无耻混蛋》（第25名）、《第九区》（第27名）、《公主与青蛙》（第32位）、《朱莉与朱莉娅》（第34位）、《鬼妈妈》（第42位）和《在云端》（第43位）获得了最佳影片或动画长片、导演、演员或编剧类主要奖项提名<ref name="boxofficemojooscars">{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?view=allmovies&yr=2009&p=.htm |title=2009 Oscar nominations and wins by movie |publisher=Amazon.com |work=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131014174745/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?view=allmovies&yr=2009&p=.htm | archivedate= 2013-10-14 | deadurl= no}}</ref>，而获得其它奖项提名的影片还有《哈利·波特与混血王子》（[[亚军|亚军]]）、《變形金剛：復仇之戰》（[[季军|季军]]）、《星际迷航》（第7名）和《大侦探福尔摩斯》（第11名）<ref name="boxofficemojooscars" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
本届颁奖典礼获得的媒体评价褒贬不一，一些媒体给出了较为负面的评价。影评人[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]批评鲍德温和马丁的开场独白“无趣得出奇”。他之后表示对《拆弹部队》胜出感到高兴，但选择鲍德温和马丁来主持实在欠妥。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/festivals-and-awards/no-pain-for-hurt-locker-bigelow |title=No pain for "Hurt Locker," Bigelow |last=Ebert |first=Roger |accessdate=2013-11-05 |date=2010-03-07 |work=Chicago Sun-Times |publisher=Sun-Times Media Group | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130603081553/http://www.rogerebert.com/festivals-and-awards/no-pain-for-hurt-locker-bigelow | archivedate= 2013-06-03 | deadurl= no}}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》专栏作家玛丽·麦克纳马拉（{{lang|en|Mary McNamara}}）打趣称节目完全没有时机感，“尽管每个人都尽了最大努力，但今年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼似乎遭遇了信任危机。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscars-review8-2010mar08,0,2236486.story |work=Los Angeles Times |publisher=Tribune Company |accessdate=2013-11-05 |date=2010-03-08 |title=Oscars show has no sense of timing |last=McNamara |first=Mary |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024151910/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/awards/oscars/la-et-oscars-review8-2010mar08%2C0%2C2236486.story |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》电影评论员詹姆斯·邦尼沃兹克（{{lang|en|James Poniewozik}}）也批评晚会的节奏上断断续续，称其是“奥斯卡的一个经典失败”。他还指出拥有两个主持人也是节目的缺点之一。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2010/03/08/the-oscarcast-classic-not-necessarily-in-a-good-way/ |title=The Oscarcast: Classic, Not Necessarily in a Good Way |first=James |last=Poniewozik |date=2010-03-08 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |work=Time |publisher=Time Warner | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20121024221252/http://entertainment.time.com/2010/03/08/the-oscarcast-classic-not-necessarily-in-a-good-way/ | archivedate= 2012-10-24 | deadurl= no}}</ref>

其它媒体对颁奖典礼的评价更为正面。《[[電視指南_(雜誌)|电影指南]]》杂志的布鲁斯·费茨（{{lang|en|Bruce Fetts}}）在其专栏中称赞了两位主持人的表现<ref>{{cite journal |last=Fetts |first=Burce |title=Cheers and Jeers |publisher=TV Guide |date=2010-03-22–28 |page=104}}</ref>。《[[芝加哥论坛报|芝加哥论坛报]]》的莫琳·瑞恩（{{lang|en|Maureen Ryan}}）给整场晚会的评价为中等，但赞扬了演员的表现<ref>{{cite news |url=http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2010/03/oscars-academy-awards-.html |title=The Oscars: A bit of razzle-dazzle, some mainstream charm and not enough NPH |date=2010-03-07 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |work=Chicago Tribune |publisher=Tribune Company| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130801024604/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2010/03/oscars-academy-awards-.html | archivedate= 2013-08-01 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

=== 收视率和获奖 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过美国广播公司在美国直播，其播出时段里平均有4162万观众收看，与[[第81届奥斯卡金像奖|去年的颁奖典礼]]相比有13%的提升<ref name="var1" />，而所有曾观看部分播出时段节目的观众总数则有约7978万<ref>{{cite news |title=ABC Draws Its Biggest Weekly Audience Since September '08 | url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news.aspx?id=20100309abc02#ixzz11nopGnyT | work=The Futon Critic | date=2010-03-10 | accessdate=2013-11-05}}</ref>。节目在尼尔森收视率调查中的成绩也好于过去两届<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/03/09/oscars-wins-weeks-ratings/ |date=2010-03-09 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |work=Entertainment Weekly |publisher=TimeWarner| last=Stransky |first=Tanner |title= Ratings: Oscar's 41 million viewers win week's top prize |archivedate=2013-05-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130507142528/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2010/03/09/oscars-wins-weeks-ratings/}}</ref>，在18至49岁年龄段人群中的收视率为13.1%，比去年提高了8%<ref>{{cite news |last=Kissell |first=Rick | title=Oscars draw 41 million viewers | url=http://variety.com/2010/scene/news/oscars-draw-41-million-viewers-1118016200/ | work=Variety | publisher=PMC | date=2010-03-08 | accessdate=2013-11-05 |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131105083139/http://variety.com/2010/scene/news/oscars-draw-41-million-viewers-1118016200/}}</ref>，是继2005年的[[第77届奥斯卡金像奖|第77届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]以来收视人数最高的一届<ref>{{cite news | author=Scott Bowles | title=Low Oscar Ratings Cue Soul-Searching |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130117050540/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2008-02-26-oscar-ratings_N.htm |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/movieawards/oscars/2008-02-26-oscar-ratings_N.htm |work=USA Today| publisher = Gannett Company | date=2008-02-26 | accessdate=2013-11-05 |archivedate=2013-01-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Finke |first=Nikki | title=Oscar Ratings: 'Avatar' Loses But ABC And AMPAS Aren't Blue Despite Greying Viewers | url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/03/oscar-ratings-add-up-for-abc/ | work=Deadline Hollywood | publisher=PMC | date=2010-03-08 | accessdate=2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120328111054/http://www.deadline.com/2010/03/oscar-ratings-add-up-for-abc/ | archivedate= 2012-03-28 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。

2010年7月，颁奖典礼获得了[[第62屆黃金時段艾美獎|第62屆黃金時段艾美獎]]的12项提名<ref>{{cite news |last=O'Neil |first=Tom | title=Emmys love for Oscars continues with 12 nominations | url=http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2010/07/emmys-love-for-oscars-continues-with-12-nominations.html | work=Los Angeles Times | publisher=Tribune Company | date=2010-07-12 | accessdate=2013-11-05 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130930112738/http://goldderby.latimes.com/awards_goldderby/2010/07/emmys-love-for-oscars-continues-with-12-nominations.html | archivedate= 2013-09-30 | deadurl= no}}</ref>，并在次月获得了综艺、音乐或纪实类节目杰出艺术指导奖<ref>{{cite news|last=Jones |first=Kenneth |title=The 2009 Tony Awards Broadcast Wins Emmy; Neil Patrick Harris Is a "Glee"-ful Winner |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/142270-The-2009-Tony-Awards-Broadcast-Wins-Emmy-Neil-Patrick-Harris-Is-a-Glee-ful-Winner |publisher=Playbill |date=2010-08-21 |accessdate=2013-11-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017192237/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/142270-The-2009-Tony-Awards-Broadcast-Wins-Emmy-Neil-Patrick-Harris-Is-a-Glee-ful-Winner |archivedate=2012-10-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

