=== 纪录片奖获奖致辞 ===
《海豚湾》获得纪录片奖，主创人员上台领奖并发表感言时，[[海豚|海豚]]训练员[[瑞克·歐貝瑞|瑞克·歐貝瑞]]拿着一面旗帜，上面印着“{{lang|en|Text Dolphin to 44144}}”（意为“编辑文本海豚发送到44144”），美国广播公司突然中断了画面，并且持续了几秒钟。《电视指南》称这一瞬间为“最快的一切”。<ref name="TV Guide, 11 Top Oscar Moments">{{cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/11-Oscar-Moments-1015915.aspx |work=TV Guide |title=11 Top Oscar Moments |accessdate=2013-11-05 |date=2010-03-08 |archivedate=2013-07-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130728153513/http://www.tvguide.com/News/11-Oscar-Moments-1015915.aspx}}</ref>

=== 沙查·巴隆·科恩被取消的短剧 ===
制片人麦康尼克和山克曼原本选择了[[沙查·巴隆·科恩|沙查·巴隆·科恩]]来担任主持人，但学院因担心其中风险而否决了<ref name="hosting" />。科恩和[[本·斯蒂勒|本·斯蒂勒]]原计划在典礼上表演一个短剧，但制片人因为担心节目会冒犯《阿凡达》的[[导演|导演]][[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]而决定将之取消。这个短剧中科恩将打扮成一名雌性[[阿凡达的虚构宇宙#纳美人|纳美人]]，而斯蒂勒则站在一旁[[翻译|翻译]]“她”所说的话，结束时科恩将宣布“她”“与詹姆斯·卡梅隆有了爱的结晶”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vulture.com/2010/03/sacha_baron_cohen_james_camero.html |title=Vulture Exclusive: To Protect James Cameron’s Feelings, Sacha Baron Cohen’s Avatar Sketch Is Cut From Oscar Telecast |accessdate=2013-11-05 |last=Brodesser-Akner |first=Claude |work=NYmag |publisher=NYmag
|date=2010-02-03 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130328050035/http://www.vulture.com/2010/03/sacha_baron_cohen_james_camero.html | archivedate= 2013-03-28 | deadurl= no}}</ref>。虽然卡梅隆表示他对这个短剧的内容感到满意<ref>{{cite news |title=James Cameron Doesn't Mind If Sacha Baron Cohen Spoofs 'Avatar' at Oscars |publisher=World Entertainment News Network |date=2010-03-04}}</ref>，但科恩的表演还是被取消了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2010/03/03/sacha-baron-cohens-planned-oscar-night-avatar-spoof-canned-by-the-academy/ |title=Sacha Baron Cohen's Planned Oscar Night 'Avatar' Spoof Canned By The Academy |accessdate=2013-11-05 |last=Loomis |first=George |publisher=Viacom Media Networks |work=MTV |date=2010-03-03 |archivedate=2013-04-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130427182112/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2010/03/03/sacha-baron-cohens-planned-oscar-night-avatar-spoof-canned-by-the-academy/}}</ref>。不过这个短剧最终由斯蒂勒打扮成纳美人进行了表演<ref name="guablog" />。

=== 原创歌曲奖表演的削减 ===
2010年2月，麦康尼克和山克曼宣布，本届颁奖典礼上将不会像之前多年的惯例那样将获得原创歌曲奖提名的几首歌曲分别进行现场表演，而是会在颁奖宣读提名作品名单时播放短小的片段<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/best-original-songs-wont-be-performed-at-academy-awards-20100217 |title=Best Original Songs Won't Be Performed at Academy Awards |work=Rolling Stone |publisher=Jann Wenner |date= 2010-02-17 |accessdate= 2013-11-05 |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20131105123441/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/best-original-songs-wont-be-performed-at-academy-awards-20100217}}</ref>。一些奥斯卡颁奖典礼的制作人员对此做法表示反对，称这有违传统，让每首歌曲的创作者们失去了一个在全世界观众面前表演的机会<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-01-27 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/02/oscar-spoilers-best-original-song-artists-not-performing/ |title=Oscar Spoilers: Best Original Song Artists Not Performing|publisher=PMC |last=Finke |first=Nikki |work=Deadline Hollywood Daily |date=2010-02-17 |accessdate= 2013-11-05 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130127043529/http://www.deadline.com/2010/02/oscar-spoilers-best-original-song-artists-not-performing/}}</ref>。

